tourBios.otherCarHigh: Earned All-Big South honors in 2010, was a 2012 GCAA Cleveland Golf/Srixon All-America Scholar and was a three-time Big South Presidential Honor Roll honoree, posting at least a 3.0 GPA for the 2009-10, 2010-11 and 2011-12 academic years.
tourBios.personal: Served as a student assistant golf coach after completing eligibility in 2012-13...MVP of high school golf, lacrosse and basketball teams...Superstitions include always wearing white golf shoes...Diehard Washington sports fan...Dream foursome would include Tiger Woods, Michael Jordan and Eminem.
